{"tid":404571,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[2018動畫化確定]Steins;gate zero命運石之門0暨科學ADV討論","createTime":"2017-09-18T08:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T12:04:55.000Z","uid":6327,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5a9970b3c3cacf8e8c14d9e33d4b02428f0bb1","tid":404571,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MKm5pBW-iRU/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FMKm5pBW-iRU%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=a6275b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://nichegamer.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/steins-gate-zero-0-2015-03-28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnichegamer.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F03%2Fsteins-gate-zero-0-2015-03-28.jpg&h=2e2c17c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/160020_0f8ca00685c5d52edde6d5ecc19773fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F160020_0f8ca00685c5d52edde6d5ecc19773fc.jpg&h=b8c1913f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本作主軸是輕小說《命運石之門 閉時曲線的碑文》描寫的「&beta; 世界線」的後續故事。在此世界線中，助手沒被拯救，其父發表時光機理論、第三次世界大戰爆發。或許這次就是要補充這中間發生的事情和是否又會做出什麼改變。就是無印23集中的未來岡部倫太郎所發生的事和如何準備<span style=\"color: red;\">命運石之門</span>世界線條件<br />\n【STAFF】<br />\n企&amp;#30011;&amp;#12539;原作：志倉千代丸<br />\n製作人：松原達也<br />\n角色設計：huke<br />\n腳本：林直孝、安本亨<br />\n<br />\n<strong>聲優:<br />\n</strong><br />\n岡部倫太郎:宮野真守<br />\n牧瀨紅莉栖:今井麻美<br />\n椎名真由理:<span style=\"color: red;\">花澤香菜</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橋田至:關智一<br />\n阿萬音鈴羽and her mom:田村由香里<br />\n比屋定真帆:矢作紗友里<br />\n椎名篝:潘惠美<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">完整中文STEINS;GATE ZERO game play網址(全中文自動遊戲影像)</span>:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av3834470/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav3834470%2F&d=qjisSiChuLuju8hXnyZbiHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=256312ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av3834470/</a><br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n目前五部作品 同一世界觀  除s;g0同c;c皆有遊戲/動畫版本 <br />\n以下用簡稱:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">chaos;head= c;h <br />\nsteins;gate=s;g   <br />\nrobotics;notes=r;n<br />\nchaos;child=c;c<br />\nsteins;gate zero=s;g0</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"42e5541af7066b6652eea175c0385d1fcdc65434","tid":404571,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"又黎?"},{"pid":"b9141f9869abbf70644ba64338c181e326b8317f","tid":404571,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Q 假如第一次接觸系列作動畫 洗唔洗補曬全部動畫or game?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A  c;h同c;c有劇情人物上既關連較多 s;g同s;g0屬於前後傳 當然有興趣可以先睇左動畫先<br />\n   目前動畫化左得:c;h s;g r;n 下年會有c;c動畫<br />\n   r;n當日常番睇會開心好多 最後有時閒既可以去玩game(c;h同r;n玩game啦)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q:依家10月新番套超自然九人組o;n同原本科學adv世界觀有冇關係?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A 冇 o;n雖然係社長親自由頭落筆到尾 不過同前面果幾作係屬於獨立世界觀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但係漫畫版食左書 兼且提到三百人委員會<br />\n社長話當再另一個平行世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q 周圍好多人傳c;c動畫好大機會出事 究竟係咩意思</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">A 銀link製作 爆死是常識吧 仲有劇情量難以處理 大吉利是講句萬一淨係做一季番</span><br />\n   <img src=\"https://images.plurk.com/sMsx-7wx1YcsbMz0k3o9DWjFYsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.plurk.com%2FsMsx-7wx1YcsbMz0k3o9DWjFYsV.jpg&h=fc1266a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e28067cba39f8952859961f9d2b41df93cfb826e","tid":404571,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:06:28.000Z","msg":"我穿越左？"},{"pid":"da9837ca1f85e0ab6ae6a4af69017103fde6577c","tid":404571,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy